                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing modified humic acid from low-rank coal, modified humic acid and application of modified humic acid in preparation of hard carbon negative electrode material",
                    "一种利用低阶煤制备改性腐植酸的方法、改性腐植酸及其在制备硬碳负极材料中的应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for preparing modified humic acid from low-rank coal, the modified humic acid and application of the modified humic acid in preparation of a hard carbon negative electrode material, and belongs to the technical field of sodium-ion battery materials. The method comprises the following steps: crushing and ball-milling low-rank raw coal to obtain pulverized coal; the method comprises the following steps: carrying out a hydrothermal reaction on pulverized coal, an alkaline substance and a composite modifier (comprising hydrogen peroxide, urea and/or polypyrrole, ammonium carbonate and/or ammonium pyrophosphate and the like), carrying out centrifugal separation on a hydrothermal reaction product to remove a bottom precipitate I, adjusting the pH value of an upper solution to be acidic, carrying out centrifugal separation to collect a bottom precipitate II, acidifying, washing and drying the precipitate II to obtain the coal powder. The modified humic acid which is low in ash content, high in oxygen-containing group content and simultaneously doped with nitrogen atoms is obtained, the hard carbon material with high sodium storage performance is obtained through carbonization, the hard carbon material is used as a hard carbon negative electrode material for a sodium ion battery, the reversible specific capacity reaches 300 mAh/g or above, and the first charge-discharge efficiency is larger than 80%."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种利用低阶煤制备改性腐植酸的方法、改性腐植酸及其在制备硬碳负极材料中的应用，属于钠离子电池材料技术领域。将低阶煤原煤经过破碎和球磨，得到煤粉；煤粉与碱性物质及复合改性剂(包括双氧水，尿素和/或聚吡咯，碳酸铵和/或焦磷酸铵等组分)进行水热反应，水热反应产物经过离心分离去除底层沉淀I，上层溶液通过调节pH至酸性后进行离心分离收集底层沉淀II，所述沉淀II经过酸化、洗涤和干燥，即得灰分含量低、含氧基团含量高，同时进行了氮原子掺杂的改性腐植酸，其经过炭化获得高储钠性能的硬碳材料，作为硬碳负极材料用于钠离子电池，其可逆比容量达到300mAh/g以上，首次充放电效率大于80％。"
                }
            ]
